Package org.javact.local

Interface Summary
ClientSideAnswerBackLocal Specifies the interface of a client-side object, which is in charge of recovering the answer for a client and updating the Future delegate of the MessageWithReply.
LocalActor Specification of actors, with the communication method.
 

Class Summary
ClientSideAnswerBackImpl Client-side object, which is in charge of recovering the answer from a server-side object, and updating the reply.
CreateCt *META-COMPONENT-LEVEL* (excepted STD).
MoveCt *META-COMPONENT-LEVEL* The standard local Move component.
ReceiveCt The receive component of an actor.
SendCt META-COMPONENT-LEVEL (excepted STD).
ServerSideAnswerBackImpl Server-side objects in charge of returning a result to a client, in case of client-server-like interaction (MessageWithReply).
